                <note rend="inline" type="source">821.6363 Barco/156: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Piles</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-08-27T09:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 27, 1928—9 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 11:33 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>81. Department’s 45, August 25, noon. Company’s representative has written
                    statement ready, but now feels he must obtain authority from his principals
                    before delivering it to me. He has telegraphed principals situation in
                    detail.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Piles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
